# --- Local / personal (not pushed) ---
# Put private notes here instead of deleting shared docs:
docs/private/
# Scratch / one-off SQL you do not want on GitHub (canonical schema stays in database/*.sql):
database/local/

# Draft internal review notes (already tracked files: run `git rm --cached <path>` once)
docs/*-REVIEW.md
